reviewText: L enjoyed this its part of chinese tv series "wing chun",  it had couple things missing a romance + explaination why young lad wanted revenge, wing chun is the complete version , l found subtitles went to fast but l still enjoyed it , l think the wing chun version is slower ,as this had a lot of fight scenes from start , someone said its not good l disagree l enjoyed this
Liked the movie, action is okay
